        <?php echo $this->stencil->setHeadline('Watch OS'); ?>
        <p><strong>Watch OS</strong> is the operating system of the <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Apple Watch', 'ITH'); ?>, developed by <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Apple Inc', 'C'); ?>. It is based on the <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('iOS', 'OS'); ?> operating system and has many features similar to those of iOS. It was first released on 24 April 2015, alongside the Apple Watch. The Apple Watch is currently the only device that runs watchOS. The API is called WatchKit. At <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('WWDC', 'IT'); ?> 2015 watchOS 2 with major improvements like support for native third-party apps was previewed and will be released fall 2015.</p>
